line_1: And Saxe himself might weep to see't.
Turn'd round so quick, you scarce cou'd see't;
line_2: The Flyer, tho't had Leaden Feet,

line_1: You'll pardon Me: — Ay, now I see't:
line_2: I did not look upon your Feet:

line_1: God bless your Honors, can ye see't,
line_2: The kind, auld, cantie Carlin greet,

line_1: God bless your Honors, can ye see't,
line_2: An' no get warmly to your feet,

line_1: God bless your Honors, can ye see't,
line_2: An' tell them, wi' a patriot-heat,
